# This file keeps the assets directory in git.
#
# The default decoder is the custom export with mask refinement support:
# - tracker-prompt-encoder-mask-decoder-with-mask-input.onnx (17MB) **default**
#
# To generate it, run the export script in serverless/pytorch/facebookresearch/sam3/nuclio/:
#   python export_decoder_with_mask_input.py --checkpoint auto --output <path>
#
# Alternatively, download pre-built decoders from usls (no mask refinement):
# wget -O tracker-prompt-encoder-mask-decoder.onnx \
#   "https://github.com/jamjamjon/assets/releases/download/sam3/tracker-prompt-encoder-mask-decoder.onnx"
